>
  <section class="cover">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span class="kicker">selected work ↓</span>
      <h1>Notes from the <em>field</em>.</h1>
      <p class="deck">Each of these started as a sentence that didn't fully describe what was needed. The job, in every case, was to find that out and then go build it.</p>
